source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_01<tab>Feltsmox has not been able to catch anything while fishing lately. She seems to think that wildebeest eyes, from the nearby wildebeests, might solve the problem. Help this discouraged and disheartened goblin by gathering three eyes from the wildebeests.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_01<tab>Feltsmox n'arrive plus à pêcher et se sent découragée. Elle vous a demandé de bien vouloir lui rapporter trois <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B1B0302 /var>, que vous pourrez obtenir en tuant des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0C0302 /var>.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_02<tab>You have gathered the mysterious, red orbs from the wildebeests you slew. Deliver them to Feltsmox and find out what she plans to do with them.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez trouvé les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B1B0302 /var>. Apportez-les à Feltsmox, comme convenu.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_03<tab>Through the tinted lenses in her mask, you see Feltsmox's eyes light up as you produce the wildebeest eyes. She explains that it makes exceptional bait for fishing, before eagerly rushing away to make use of it.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_SEQ_03<tab>Visiblement Feltsmox a l'intention d'utiliser les yeux comme appâts. Elle espère ainsi sortir de sa mauvaise passe...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_TODO_00<tab>Slay wildebeests and obtain their eyes.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_TODO_00<tab>Abattre des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0C0302 /var> pour récupérer leurs yeux

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the wildebeest eyes to Feltsmox.

TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_000Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Nothing is going well for Feltsmox, so she goes for a walk, but Feltsmox is still unhappy.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_000<tab>Psssh, psshh... Feltsmox se balade au gré du vent... Mais Feltsmox ne se sent pas mieux pour autant, elle est triste...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_001<tab>Feltsmox loves fishing, but is having <var 1A 02 /var>terrible<var 1A 01 /var> luck when fishing in recent days. Feltsmox can't catch <var 1A 02 /var>anything<var 1A 01 /var>!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_001<tab>Feltsmox voudrait pêcher ses poissons tran<var 16 /var>quil<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment... Mais elle n'y arrive pas.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_002<tab>Feltsmox has an idea. Uplander, please help! Kill wildebeests and collect three of their eyes.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_002<tab>Feltsmox aimerait qu'on lui ramène trois yeux de <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0C0202 /var><var 1D /var>! Il suffit d'aller en chasser.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_010<tab>Please help, uplander. Please collect three wildebeest eyes from nearby wildebeests.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_010<tab>Feltsmox aimerait qu'on lui ramène trois yeux de <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0C0202 /var><var 1D /var>! Il suffit d'aller en chasser.

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_100_020Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Excellent! Perhaps this time Feltsmox will finally catch something!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_100_020<tab>Psssh, psssh<var 1D /var>! Merci, merci<var 1D /var>! Avec ça, le moral de Feltsmox va remonter d'un coup<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_021<tab>These sparkly, shiny orbs make best fishingbait. Feltsmox will catch some big, delicious fish with this... Feltsmox will try it right now!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ803_01933_FELTSMOX_000_021<tab>Ces yeux tout mous vont faire d'excellents appâts<var 1D /var>! Avec ça, ça va mordre, pour sûr<var 1D /var>!
